					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="Job Recruiters Aren't Taking Advantage of Social Media in Their Search for Rockstar Hires" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20151217172915-young-woman-recruitment-interview-hiring-applicant-meeting-candidate-apply.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
